I'm off to sleep as well. Goodnight everyone.

::Killfest/EndBringer/Demise/Greven::

Killfest nods, motioning for Greven and Demise to get going. The two 
bots go back into the tunnel that Killfest had emerged from, heading 
to the Predacon base. Killfest and EndBringer board Astroblast.

"Allright, let's get going." Killfest says.
